<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">١٦٥) باذام أبو صالح مولى أم هانئ:</span> ضعيف يرسل <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c1">"فيه مقال"</span>. <span class="c1">"الخبر"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٣٢)</span>. <span class="c1">"مضعف"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٦٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"مشهور بالضعف"</span>. <span class="c1">"الخصال"</span> <span class="c2">(٦٨)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٧٤)</span>، و<span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(١٠/ ٥٤٩)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c1">"متروك"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٥٦٣)</span>. <span class="c1">"متروك الحديث"</span>. <span class="c1">"المهرة"</span> <span class="c2">(١٨/ ١٥)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">١٦٦) بَجَالة بن عَبَدة التميمي العنبري البصري:</span> ثقة <span class="c2">(خ د ت س)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c1">"تابعي كبير بصري ثقة"</span>. <span class="c1">"الخبر"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٩)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">١٦٧) بَحر بن كنيز السقاء أبو الفضل البصري:</span> ضعيف <span class="c2">(ق)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c1">"أحد الضعفاء"</span>. <span class="c1">"اللسان"</span> <span class="c2">(٧/ ٣٣١)</span>.<span class="c5"> ترجمة:</span> الوليد بن عيسى.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٣٠١)</span>، و <span class="c2">(٣/ ٣٤٨)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c1">"متروك"</span>. <span class="c1">"التغليق"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ٢٢٧)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">١٦٨) بحر بن نصر بن سابق الخولاني مولاهم:</span> ثقة <span class="c2">(كن)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c1">"من الثقات"</span>. <span class="c1">"الخصال"</span> <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">١٦٩) البختري بن عبيد الطابخي الكلبي الشامي:</span> ضعيف متروك <span class="c2">(ق)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"الكشاف "</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٤٧٣)</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">١٧٠) بدر بن عمرو بن جراد السعدي والد الربيع:</span> مجهول <span class="c2">(ق)</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c1">"مجهول"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ١٧٧)</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">١٧١) بَدَل بن المحبر أبو المُنِير البصري:</span> ثقة ثبت، إلا في حديثه عن زائدة <span class="c2">(خ ٤)</span>.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>